{"type":null,"faqId":45293,"title":"如何安装荣耀盒子M321？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164821\" style=\"width:3.6604166in;height:3.0819445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>用 HDMI 线将盒子连接至高清电视机的 HDMI in 接口。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>接通电源，盒子指示灯点亮，自动开机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>打开电视，用电视机遥控器切换电视信号源至连接盒子的 HDMI 输入。此时电视画面将显示盒子开机画面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>根据画面提示，完成开机设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":242,"faqType":"安装产品","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"814","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Setting-Up","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556870000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":44,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"安装,连接高清电视,荣耀盒子","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}